code: function script_scoreSadir(rows){let rates=getRatesFromRows(rows);let ratesBySubject=orderBySubject(rates);console.log(ratesBySubject);}function getRatesFromRows(rows){let rates=rows.map(row=>{return row._rawData[2];});return rates;}function orderBySubject(rates){let newRates=[rates[0]];let index=0;rates.forEach(rate=>{if(rate!==rates[index]){newRates.push(rate);}index++;});return newRates;}export{script_scoreSadir};
